keywords:
  - large language models
  - economic elasticities
  - belief elicitation
  - taxable income elasticity
  - optimal taxation
abstract: >-
  Elicitation harness, 10,140-run dataset, and paper studying the
  prompt-conditioned response distributions that 26 frontier large
  language models from nine organizations produce when asked about 26
  economic elasticities under a fixed structured-output protocol with
  15 repeated runs per model-quantity cell.
